# Product Info List UI (Client Preference)

When showing product detail information (details, fragrance notes, shipping/returns, precautions, etc.), use a **minimal accordion list**:

- Full-width rows separated by thin horizontal lines (top, between, bottom)
- Left-aligned section titles only when collapsed (no plus/arrow icons required)
- Click a row → content smoothly expands/unfolds beneath it
- Expanded content can include subheadings, key-value lines, paragraphs, and numbered lists
- Other sections stay collapsed unless opened; headers shift down as content opens

Do not replace this with static long-form blocks or card-based FAQ layouts unless the client changes direction.
